 306:Sensor/dht11_sim.c **** 
 307:Sensor/dht11_sim.c **** /**
 308:Sensor/dht11_sim.c ****  * dht11_tim1_cc_irq - TIM1 CC ISR, thực thi TX state machine
 309:Sensor/dht11_sim.c ****  *
